Global Salmonella Culture Medium Market Insights
Salmonella Culture Medium Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Salmonella Culture Medium Market Overview
The global Salmonella Culture Medium market size was valued at approximately USD 250 million in 2024 and is expected to grow at a steady compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6% from 2025 to 2030. The growing demand for food safety testing and the increasing prevalence of foodborne diseases are driving market growth. Moreover, the rising focus on healthcare and microbiological research is fueling the development of advanced culture mediums. As the need for rapid and accurate detection of Salmonella strains continues to rise, the market for Salmonella culture mediums will witness further growth. The demand is also rising in clinical diagnostics, biotechnology research, and food & beverage industries. Global market expansion, particularly in developing regions, is expected to significantly contribute to market revenue during the forecast period.

